DOMAIN-SUFFIX,115cdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,123pan.com

# =========================
# Railway / Transport
# =========================
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,12306.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,95306.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,china-railway.com.cn

# =========================
# DingTalk
# =========================
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dingtalk.com
