# =========================
# CN GEO Fallback (must be last)
# =========================
GEOIP,CN,DIRECT

# =========================
# Design Notes
# - DOMAIN rules take priority over GEOIP via ordering
# - GEOIP is used only as fallback
# - Removed overly broad qq.com scope for safety
# - Maintained minimal stable domain set
# =========================